name: What is going on in my head, Remember the flight, the bird dies.
description:
Remember the flight, the bird dies.
This collection is under construction and my intention from this collection is that despite the appearance of human beings, things happen in their minds, complexity is seen, sometimes happy and sometimes sad and dissatisfied, in this work you can change your mood.
